tarctica for accelerated ecosystem responses to climate warming, confirming similar observations in the Northern Hemisphere. Our findings support the hypothesis that future warming will trigger significant changes in these fragile Antarctic ecosystems.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Cannone, Nicoletta", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Malfasi, Francesco", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Favero-Longo, Sergio Enrico", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Convey, Peter", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Guglielmin, Mauro", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Chapter 1", "biodiversity", "environment assessment", "IPBES", "Alien Invasive Species Assessment AIS", "invasive species"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/d8dec3aff851df97267d96d1a40736a8", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/c53cdf077cda181a084ef3737907d879e2639688ec8a6ca2941b470d7a94d33d", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/2352922/items/E6PDTMIC", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/2352922/items/E6PDTMIC", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/371b2a02bc6fbf2c1de260e4c38e39f5!/b94354-96473", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/359bd494433933b868f85e88d3437f76", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.1016/j.cub.2022.01.074", "relation": "isVariantFormOf", "resource_type": "publication", "scheme": "doi"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.7430682", "relation": "isCitedBy", "resource_type": "publication-report", "scheme": "doi"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "7", "pages": "1599-1606.e2", "title": "Current Biology", "volume": "3